{"title":"你的遗志  悼陈团长宗尧同志","authors":["篷放"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":11,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的遗志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悼陈团长宗尧同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"篷放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能忘记眉山下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斑江岸上的月夜里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由于战场上血流过多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面色惨白的你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已失掉了讲话的力气；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但把身边唯一珍贵的东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那从敌人手中夺来的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗了终身的武器——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你心爱的卜朗宁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默地交给王司令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作为永别的纪念品。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在泪水模糊中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看不清你的遗容；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是我看见了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲忿已极的王震将军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把那支卜朗宁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧地握在手里；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛就要向仇敌射去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的同志宗尧："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我已深深地知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是你的意志——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那坚强的战斗的心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要我们用自己的武器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为受难的中国人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把国民党反动派坚决扫清！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在毛泽东旗帜下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设起人民的新国家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四五，六，于湖南小眉战斗后草稿"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}